    <p>Book a boat and learn how to sail with the best local captains. Listen about their experiences
    sailing around the world.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="black-cards-container d-flex">
    <div class="main-black-card">
      <%= cl_image_tag "3583747_17113002580060046821_b956oc", heigh: 500, width: 500, crop: :fill %>
      <p>More than 1,000 water sports athletes have already acquired driver's licenses for sailing or/and motor boats in this water sports school!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="right-black-cards" style="width: 100%">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-around">
        <div class="small-black-card">
          <%= cl_image_tag "Screen_Shot_2020-07-17_at_21.59.36_kspmzp", :height=>200, :crop=>"scale" %>
          <p>Learn how to sail with the bests sailors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="small-black-card">
          <%= cl_image_tag "Screen_Shot_2020-07-17_at_21.58.33_ruda7t", :height=>200, :crop=>"scale" %>
          <p>Experience a boat life style while enjoying great holidays.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="small-black-card">
          <%= cl_image_tag "Screen_Shot_2020-07-17_at_22.51.19_gqgqh5", :width=>218, :crop=>"scale" %>
          <p>Have a great time while diving with sharks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="large-black-card">
        <%= cl_image_tag "Screen_Shot_2020-07-17_at_22.56.44_hbl1zk", :width=>700, :crop=>"scale"%>
        <p>With us you will have an unforgettable experience guaranteed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

